
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zxx">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="description" content="Male_Fashion Template">
    <meta name="keywords" content="Male_Fashion, unica, creative, html">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>DangKhoa | Template</title>

    <!-- Google Font -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Asset/font-awesome-4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <!-- Css Styles -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/css/bootstrap.min.css" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/css/elegant-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/css/magnific-popup.css" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/css/nice-select.css" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/css/owl.carousel.min.css" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/css/slicknav.min.css" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/css/style.css" type="text/css">
    <style>
        .mini_cart {
            position: absolute;
            height: auto;
            background-color: black;
            right: 0;
            width: 396px;
            z-index: 3;
            display: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .header__top {
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background: #9CC6DE !important;
        }

        @@keyframes slide {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(-100%);
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateX(100%);
                opacity: 1;
                display:none;
            }
        }

        .animated-text {
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: slide 20s linear infinite;
        }

        .header__top__left p {
            color: black !important;
            font-weight: 600 !important;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div style="position:relative;">
        <div id="get_blur">
        </div>
        <!-- Page Preloder -->
        <div id="preloder">
            <div class="loader"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Offcanvas Menu Begin -->
        <div class="offcanvas-menu-overlay"></div>
        <div class="offcanvas-menu-wrapper">
            <div class="offcanvas__option">
                @*<div class="offcanvas__links">
                <a href="#">Sign in</a>
                <a href="#">FAQs</a>
                </div>
                <div class="offcanvas__top__hover">
                <span>USD <i class="fa fa-arrow-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                <ul>
                <li>USD</li>
                <li>EUR</li>
                <li>USD</li>
                </ul>
                </div>*@
            </div>
            <div class="offcanvas__nav__option">
                <a href="#" class="search-switch"><img src="~/Content/img/icon/search.png" alt=""></a>
                @*<a href="#"><i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i></a>*@
                <a class="cart_icon" href="#"><img src="~/Content/img/icon/cart.png" alt=""> <span class="conut-number"></span></a>
                <div class="price">$0.00</div>
            </div>
            <div id="mobile-menu-wrap">
            </div>
            <div class="offcanvas__text">
                <p>Địa chỉ:Số nhà 117,Đường 419,KCNTT_HN.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Offcanvas Menu End -->
        <!-- Header Section Begin -->
        <header class="header">
            <div class="header__top">
                @*<div class="container">*@
                    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">
                        <div class="header__top__left text-nowrap animated-text">
                            <p>Vật tư xây dựng Sằn Liên. Chuyên vật tư ngành nước , đồ cứu hỏa ,ống thép mạ kẽm. Địa chỉ: Số nhà 117 - Đường 419 - KCNTT_HN.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                @*</div>*@
            </div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3">
                        <div class="header__logo">
                            <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Home")"><img src="/Content/img/logo.jpg" alt=""></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                        <nav class="header__menu mobile-menu">
                            <ul>
                                <li><a href="/Home">Trang chủ</a></li>
                                <li><a href="/Events">Sản Phẩm</a></li>
                                <li>
                                    <a href="#">Trang</a>
                                    <ul class="dropdown">
                                        <li><a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Carts")">Giỏ hàng</a></li>
                                        <li><a href="@Url.Action("Infor", "Order")">Tra cứu đơn</a></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                                <li><a href="#">Liên lạc</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </nav>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3">
                        <div class="header__nav__option">
                            <a href="#" class="search-switch"><img src="~/Content/img/icon/search.png" alt=""></a>
                            <a href="#"><img src="~/Content/img/icon/heart.png" alt=""></a>
                            <a class="cart_icon" href="#"><img src="~/Content/img/icon/cart.png" alt=""> <span class="conut-number"></span></a>
                            <div class="price">đ0.00</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="canvas__open"><i class="fa fa-bars"></i></div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Header Section End -->
        <!-- THIS THING -->
        <div class="all_render">
            <div class="mini_cart" id="mini_cart_id">
                <span class="triangle-up"></span>
                <h5 class="cart-sub-title" style="margin-top:12px">
                    Thêm gần đây
                    <span id="cart_icon_close" style="margin-right:6px">
                        <button style="border:none;background-color: wheat">X</button>
                    </span>
                </h5>
                <div class="cart-sub-render">
                    @*<div class="cart-sub">
                    <img class="image-cart-sub" src="~/Content/img/hang1.jpg" />
                    <div>
                    <span>Áo hồng - 3</span>
                    <p>Số lượng : 1</p>
                    <button class="cart__close button-remove-cart-sub">
                    Remove
                    </button>
                    </div>
                    </div>*@
                </div>
                <div class="cart-sub-total">
                    @*<button class="cart-sub-button"> Checkout </button>*@
                    <a class="cart-sub-button" href="@Url.Action("Index", "Carts")">Giỏ hàng </a>
                    <a class="cart-sub-button" href="@Url.Action("Infor", "Order")">Tra cứu đơn </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            @RenderBody()

        </div>
        <!-- THIS THING -->
        <!-- Footer Section Begin -->
        <footer class="footer">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                        <div class="footer__about">
                            <div class="footer__logo">
                                <a href="#"><img src="#" alt=""></a>
                            </div>
                            <p>Khách hàng là trung tâm của mô hình kinh doanh độc đáo của chúng tôi, bao gồm cả thiết kế.</p>
                            <a href="#"><img src="#" alt=""></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-2 offset-lg-1 col-md-3 col-sm-6">
                        <div class="footer__widget">
                            <h6>Shopping</h6>
                            <ul>
                                <li><a href="#">Ống nhựa</a></li>
                                <li><a href="#">Ống Kẽm</a></li>
                                <li><a href="#">Phụ kiện gia dụng</a></li>
                                <li><a href="#">Đồ điện tử</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-3 col-sm-6">
                        <div class="footer__widget">
                            <h6>Mua sắm</h6>
                            <ul>
                                <li><a href="#">Liên hệ</a></li>
                                <li><a href="#">Phương thức thanh toán</a></li>
                                <li><a href="#">Giao hàng</a></li>
                                <li><a href="#">Hoàn trả</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3 offset-lg-1 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
